src:
Winning numbers drawn in 'Lucky For Life' game
05 Nov 2019, 04:28 by The Associated Press
ROCKY HILL, Conn. (AP) _ The winning numbers in Monday evening's drawing of the "Lucky For Life" game were:
28-34-42-44-48, Lucky Ball: 15
(twenty-eight, thirty-four, forty-two, forty-four, forty-eight; Lucky Ball: fifteen)
